CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772975481
OL,3,CMan arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,4,Cafter death of woman
OL,6,FDetective Inspector Rob Underhill
OL,7,Fsaid: "The investigation is still in
OL,8,Fits early stages; however, an arrest
OL,9,Fhas been made, and we are not seeking
OL,10,Fanyone else in connection with the
OL,11,Fincident.
OL,13,F"I want to reassure the community that
OL,14,Fthere is no risk to the wider public.
OL,16,F"Members of the public are likely to
OL,17,Fsee an increased police presence while
OL,18,Fwe continue to investigate, and we
OL,19,Fwould advise anyone with any concerns
OL,20,Fto please speak to one of our
OL,21,Funiformed officers."
